Cat
    movesLeft: whenLeftArrowKeyPressed
    movesRight: whenRightArrowKeyPressed
    
     
Mouse
    appearRandomly: fromPosition [(x=-202 to 206), Y= 135)];
    moveToDirectionOfCat: 2 steps
    getDeleted: whenTouchingBallOrEdge

Ball/Gun

    Shoots: whenSpacebarPressed
    KillsMouse: whenTouchesTheMouse
    disappears: whenTochingMouseOrEdge

Lives

    atGameStart: SetsToThree
    ReducesByOne: whenMouseTouchEdge
    whenLivesEqualsZero: GameOver

Level

    changeInLevel: ChangesSpeedOfMouseApperance
    atGameStart: SetsToZero
    forEveryTwentyScore: LevelIncreaseByOne

Score

    ScoreRegisters: CountOfMouseKilled